{

    "resource_manager": "SLURM",

      "name": "hello_jobstep",
      "path": "$MYSCRATCH/hello_jobstep/hello_jobstep"
    },
    "execution_command": "srun -l -u -N 1 -n 1 -c 8 --gpus-per-node=1 --gpus-per-task=1 ${theExe} | sort -n"
